e":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:49:14.000Z","msg":"東南亞，歐洲快跟隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d302f7ba9c63733dbbbda68dd239e332484c736","tid":2150882,"uid":20170,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:50:00.000Z","msg":"邱騰華一到店，所有喝酒的人便都看着他笑，有的叫道，「邱騰華，你的單獨關稅區又被美帝收皮了！」他不回答，對櫃裏說，「來樽腐乳，要基本土法泡製的。」便排出九文大錢。他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又偷了人家的關稅優惠！」邱騰華睜大眼睛說，「你怎麼這樣憑空汚人清白&hellip;&hellip;」「什麼清白？我前天親眼見你偷了美國的關稅優惠，吊着打。」邱騰華便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，「關稅不能算偷&hellip;&hellip;關稅！自由貿易國際市場&hellip;&hellip;的事，能算偷麼？」接連便是難懂的話，什麼「單獨關稅區」，什麼「基本法賦予」之類，引得衆人都鬨笑起來：店內外充滿了快活的空氣。"},{"pid":"e2bc929f47f5ca91067faf41fca6d2ceb9d815dd","tid":2150882,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:51:30.000Z","msg":"香港係基本法&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;唔講了"},{"pid":"5c1405d464f70318d9ac5b9da4bd5ae4c2396a66","tid":2150882,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:52:21.000Z","msg":"溫支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一個終國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"030945b6002cfc747269742e92f95751f5eded21","tid":2150882,"uid":268591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:54:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4683e544658470fadc51f9e662c1c567a0a3e3fc","tid":2150882,"uid":283222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:55:22.000Z","msg":"祖國咁照顧香港，香港人邊洗做嫁，MADE乜鬼HK<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c582a98f3df